    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mazey Village, A Cozy Adventure Awaits 🌿</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tornado has scattered belongings and broken homes across a once-peaceful town. As a skilled maze navigator, it’s up to you to explore, recover what was lost, and rebuild the village into something even better than before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766240/extras/a72385c28ba7056a7745b516068f903d.poster.avif?t=1762500582\" width=800 height=333 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766240/extras/a72385c28ba7056a7745b516068f903d.webm?t=1762500582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore a World of Hidden Treasures ✨</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through forests, ruins, and snowy landscapes while mapping the mazes. Recover lost treasures, meet cozy creatures, and uncover delightful surprises around every corner.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for belongings hidden across the maze world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Befriend villagers and talking animals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with tiny critters who lend a hand.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766240/extras/03f6c08cccda9a35c2f7bb3f9c6e4a88.poster.avif?t=1762500582\" width=800 height=333 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766240/extras/03f6c08cccda9a35c2f7bb3f9c6e4a88.webm?t=1762500582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rebuild and Customize the Village 🏡</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design the town your way by placing decorations, shaping its layout, and creating a cozy space that matches your style. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restore homes and welcome villagers back.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate with furniture, gardens, and charming details.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the village flourish as you bring the community together!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766240/extras/739ddfc55b9f37e84f8dad09f621b4fb.poster.avif?t=1762500582\" width=800 height=333 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766240/extras/739ddfc55b9f37e84f8dad09f621b4fb.webm?t=1762500582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A World Full of Life 🐮</strong><br><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From petting cows and penguins to uncovering hidden stories, <strong>Mazey Village</strong> is full of little moments that make every step special.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to begin your journey? <strong>The village is waiting for you!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766240/extras/12243cde800aea5f5b236f69722b566e.poster.avif?t=1762500582\" width=780 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766240/extras/12243cde800aea5f5b236f69722b566e.webm?t=1762500582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p>",
